Hello Sir,

We would like to apprise you about our summer internships program for the
students enrolled in Computer Science programs. We would really
appreciate,if you could distribute the following links among all the
students enrolled in the Computer Science programs at your university.  You
can find the details about our company and the internships program below.

* Link to internship posting: http://kitboard.co/internships2016

* Link to internship application: http://kitboard.co/internships2016/apply

* About our Company: http://kitboard.co/about
*About KitBoard Inc.*

KitBoard Inc. is a Canadian Technology Startup based on a future Internet
research project at the University of Toronto. We are building a smart
enterprise application that will help enterprise workers to quickly derive
actionable insights from the vast array of information to be generated by
the enterprise devices that will be connected to Internet in next decade.
Our application imbibes our research in complex technologies, viz. Internet
of things, future networks, machine learning, and cloud computing, in one
easily configurable, deployable, and manageable application. Our data
science driven application will assist enterprise workers of tomorrow to
take smart data driven decisions for completing their day-to-day tasks.

Some selected research paper published by our team can be found here  (Just
a representative list)


   1. ITS Canada: https://goo.gl/VwUrzL
   2. ACM  DEBs : http://goo.gl/jJdP7L
   3. Software Defined Office: http://goo.gl/iuEKFb
   4. Application platform for Smart Transportation: http://goo.gl/yxIlDS
